Description: The Early Intervention in Psychosis Waiting Times data contains information on the number of people with first episode of psychosis who have accessed or are waiting for treatment.
Name: The Early Intervention in Psychosis Waiting Times data
Route from landing page to data: Data can be located on the landing page under England Time-Series, CSV File x 2 and the current year 2019/2020
Sizing Notes: A simple table with simple dimensions.  A CSV file is available for The time series of EIP data from December 2015 to present and a seperate CSV file for the current time series.  May be better suited to the mental health family.
